<!-- ==================== EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ==================== -->
<section>
    <h2>Executive Summary</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">Everything your event company needs, in one cross-platform mobile app.</p>

    <p>This is a <strong>fully developed, cross-platform mobile application</strong> designed specifically for event management companies. It covers every aspect of event operations &mdash; from member recruitment and onboarding, through event planning and execution, to payment processing and performance analytics.</p>

    <p>The app is <strong>production-ready</strong> and has been actively used in real-world event operations. It runs on both <strong>iOS and Android</strong> from a single codebase, with a cloud backend that handles authentication, real-time data, file storage, push notifications, and analytics.</p>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <h3>What You're Getting</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>A complete mobile app that would take <strong>6&ndash;12 months</strong> and <strong>$30,000&ndash;$80,000+</strong> to build from scratch</li>
            <li>Battle-tested in real event operations</li>
            <li>Ready to deploy under your own brand</li>
            <li>Fully customizable to match your workflow</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

