<!-- ==================== CORE FEATURES ==================== -->
<section>
    <h2>Core Features</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">A comprehensive suite of tools designed for every aspect of event operations.</p>

    <!-- Feature 1: User Management -->
    <h3><span class="section-number">01.</span> User Management &amp; Onboarding</h3>
    <div class="screenshot-gallery">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7229.PNG?alt=media&token=bef2115b-3772-499a-9b48-df13bfe742c1" alt="Signup Flow Step 1">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7230.PNG?alt=media&token=c4542e6d-530e-4926-8753-1d51bbc62b61" alt="Signup Flow Step 2">
</div>
    <p>A comprehensive member management system that handles the entire lifecycle from application to active membership.</p>

    <h4>Multi-Step Registration</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Detailed personal information collection (name, contact, address in English &amp; Arabic)</li>
        <li>National ID verification with photo upload (front &amp; back)</li>
        <li>Emergency contact information</li>
        <li>Education and professional background</li>
        <li>Multiple photo uploads (selfie, formal, casual) with automatic compression</li>
        <li>Clothing sizes, language skills, and additional qualifications</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Role-Based Access Control</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Members</strong> &mdash; View assigned events, participate, submit feedback, track earnings</li>
        <li><strong>Account Managers</strong> &mdash; Create events, manage teams, oversee operations</li>
        <li><strong>Admins</strong> &mdash; Full system control, analytics, user management, financial oversight</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>User Approval Workflow</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>New members submit applications with full documentation</li>
        <li>Admin review and approval process</li>
        <li>Status tracking: Pending &rarr; Approved &rarr; Active</li>
        <li>Warning system for policy violations</li>
        <li>Account suspension capability with reason tracking</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="screenshot-gallery">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7235.PNG?alt=media&token=e5ec2a03-4047-4578-ac4e-cefd93cbc396" alt="User Profile Screen">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7236.PNG?alt=media&token=d977cc9a-f4df-4f93-a193-de90aaf1b284" alt="User Profile Details">
</div>

    <h4>Member Profiles</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>40+ data fields per member</li>
        <li>Photo gallery (selfie, formal, casual, ID documents)</li>
        <li>Event participation history</li>
        <li>Earnings and payment tracking</li>
        <li>Performance metrics and analytics</li>
        <li>Warning and compliance records</li>
        <li>Group/team assignments</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <!-- Feature 2: Event Management -->
    <h3><span class="section-number">02.</span> Event Management</h3>
    <div class="screenshot-gallery">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7239.PNG?alt=media&token=8da34448-86aa-4f4d-a087-1d22f776034d" alt="Events List View">
