    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7241.PNG?alt=media&token=b186e36c-c2e2-4fad-bd4c-58e7e5cc56db" alt="Event Modules">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7242.PNG?alt=media&token=dcc1eb58-b391-49e7-b600-c2f8fa5bbc5f" alt="Event Team">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7243.PNG?alt=media&token=65c11778-b948-4e8d-b560-298899042fb1" alt="Event Settings">
    <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/ocd-co.firebasestorage.app/o/ocd_screeenshots%2FIMG_7244.PNG?alt=media&token=d9857f6a-1029-4b58-a2c3-75f4fcc55b39" alt="Event Status">
</div>
    <p>The heart of the platform &mdash; a complete event lifecycle management system with <strong>13+ configurable modules</strong> that can be toggled on or off per event.</p>

    <h4>Event Creation &amp; Setup</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Event name, date, time, and duration</li>
        <li>Location and venue details</li>
        <li>Client/company assignment</li>
        <li>Dress code specifications</li>
        <li>Transportation arrangements</li>
        <li>Accommodation details</li>
        <li>Working hours and salary information</li>
        <li>Per diem and additional compensation</li>
